##THEME
The theme of this website is *Travel & Tourism*, focused on inspiring people to explore beautiful places around the world.  

##FEATURES
1.Beautiful responsive landing page
2.Navigation bar with smooth scrolling
3.Travel packages section with images & details
4.Beginner-friendly clean and simple code
5.Sticky navigation bar
6.Footer with contact details & social links

##BREAKPOINTS
Desktop- 1024px and above | Full layout with horizontal navigation |
Tablet- 768px – 1023px | Grid adjusts, text resizes |
Mobile-320px – 767px | Menus stack vertically, sections become single column |

##HOW TO RUN/VIEW
# Using VS Code
1. Open VS Code
2. Install extension (Live Server)
3. Right-click on "index.html"
4. Click (Open with Live Server)
5. Website opens automatically in browser


